1. Install Msys, link: https://www.msys2.org/
2. Install pacman packages: `pacman -S mingw-w64-x86_64-toolchain`
3. Install glfw, glew, freeglut and opengl packages: `pacman -S mingw-w64-x86_64-glfw mingw-w64-x86_64-glew mingw-w64-x86_64-freeglut`
4. Add msys mingw64 toolchain in Settings/Build, Execution, Deployment/Toolchains, path should be: 'C:\msys64\mingw64'
5. Add mingw64 compiler of C and C++ as well, path should be: 'C:\msys64\mingw64\bin\gcc.exe' and 'C:\msys64\mingw64\bin\g++.exe'
6. Load changes and apply (the updated toolchain should be visible in the list and !! AT THE TOP OF THE LIST !! otherwise it won't work)